Hin nay, trn mt thu bao vin thng, c rt nhiu dch v gi tr gia tng

Hnh 1.1. Qu trnh khai ph tri thc trong CSDL
Qu trnh khai ph d liu tri qua 3 bc chnh sau:
Bc 1: Chun b d liu.

liu sau bc chun b ny s nh hn, x l nhanh chng hn. Chun b d liu
bao gm cc cng on sau:
- Lc d liu (Data cleaning): Loi b d liu nhiu, d liu khng thch hp.
- Tch hp d liu(Data integration): Tch hp d liu t cc ngun khc nhau.
- Chn d liu (Data selection): Chn nhng d liu lin quan trc tip n
nhim v.

1.2. CC M HNH KHAI PH D LIU
Ni chung, c hai m hnh khai ph d liu: suy din v m t [17]. Suy din

1.2.1. Khai ph d liu suy din
a. Phn lp

dng xy dng cc b phn lp d liu. Phn lp d liu c vai tr quan trng
trong tin trnh d bo cc khuynh hng, quy lut pht trin.

- Bc th nht: Da vo tp hp d liu hun luyn, xy dng mt m hnh

1.2.2. Khai ph d liu m t
a. Gom cm
Gom cm d liu hay phn cm d liu l nhm cc i tng tng t nhau
trong tp d liu vo cc cm sao cho cc i tng trong cng mt cm l tng
ng nhau cn cc i tng thuc cc cm khc nhau th khng tng ng.
Gom cm l mt v d v phng php hc khng c gim st. Trong phn lp
d liu, bn ghi thuc v lp no l phi xc nh trc, trong khi phn cm khng
xc nh trc. Trong gom cm, nhng i tng c nhm li cng nhau da vo
s ging nhau ca chng, khng th bit kt qu cc cm thu c s nh th no
khi bt u qu trnh. S ging nhau gia nhng i tng c xc nh bi
nhng hm nh gi s tng t. Thng thng nhng hm nh lng nh hm o
khong cch, hm xc nh o, c xc nh bi nhng chuyn gia trong lnh
vc chuyn mn ca mnh.
a s cc ng dng phn cm c s dng trong s phn chia th trng, phn
on khch hng, nhn dng mu, phn loi trang Web,.... Vi s phn chia khch
hng vo trong tng cm, nhng doanh nghip c th cung cp nhng dch v khc
8
nhau ti tng cm khch hng mt cch thun li. V d, da vo cc dch v in

b. Lut kt hp
Agrawal v nhm nghin cu a ra khi nim lut kt hp nm 1993 [9].

Mt lut kt hp X Y phn nh s xut hin ca tp X dn n s xut hin
ng thi tp Y. Lut kt hp l dng lut kh n gin nhng li mang nhiu
ngha v thng tin m n mang li h tr khng nh trong qu trnh ra quyt nh.

1.4. KHAI PH LUT KT HP
Khai ph lut kt hp nhm mc ch tm ra nhng MDL xut hin cng nhau
vi tn sut xut hin thng xuyn nh th no trong khi lng ln cc giao tc
ca CSDL cho trc.
Bi ton khai ph lut kt hp trn mt CSDL c chia thnh hai bi ton
nh. Bi ton th nht l tm tt c cc tp MDL thng xuyn theo ngng ti
thiu cho trc, cn gi l bi ton khai ph tp cc tp MDL thng xuyn. Bi
14
ton th hai l tm ra nhng lut kt hp t nhng tp MDL thng xuyn tha
tin cy ti thiu cho trc.
Khi c kt qu ca bi ton th nht th bi ton th 2 tr nn n gin. Gi
s ta c tp MDL thng xuyn X, tm ra nhng lut kt hp tha tin cy ti
thiu C
0

lut c tin cy tha mn.
Nh vy gii quyt bi ton khai ph lut kt hp ch tp trung vo bi ton
th nht: Khai ph tp thng xuyn.
1.4.1. Cch tip cn khai ph lut kt hp
Lnh vc khai ph lut kt hp c rt nhiu ngi quan tm v c nhiu
kt qu c cng b. C nhng xut nhm ci thin phc tp ca thut ton,
c xut li nhm mc ch tm ra nhng lut kt hp c ngha hn,
Mt s loi lut kt hp:
Lut kt hp nh phn (Binary association rule): trong dng lut ny cc MDL
ch c quan tm l c hay khng xut hin trong CSDL giao tc m khng quan
tm v tn xut xut hin.
Lut kt hp c thuc tnh s v thuc tnh hng mc (Quantitative and
categorial association rule): CSDL thc t thng c cc thuc tnh a dng (nh
phn, s, hng mc,). V vy khai ph lut kt hp cc CSDL ny cc nh
nghin cu xut mt s phng php ri rc ha nhm chuyn dng d liu ny
v dng nh phn c th p dng cc thut ton c.
Lut kt hp m (fuzzy association rule): cc nh nghin cu xut lut kt
hp m khc phc cc kh khn gp phi khi ri rc ha cc CSDL thc t.
Lut kt hp vi thuc tnh c nh trng s (association rules with
weighted items): Khi cc MDL trong CSDL c quan trng khng ng u th
mi MDL s c nh trng s theo mc xc nh quan trng ca n. Nh vy
ta c th tm c cc lut kt hp him (lut c h tr thp nhng mang
nhiu ngha).
Ta c th phn loi cc thut ton tm lut kt hp theo hai tiu ch:

Vi phng php duyt qua khng gian tm kim c phn lm 2 cch: Duyt
theo chiu rng (Breadth First Search - BFS) v duyt theo chiu su (Depth First
Search - DFS).

1.5.3. Mt s thut ton phn cm
1.5.3.1. Thut ton K-means
Thut ton k-means l thut ton phn cm c s dng ph bin nht.
tng ca thut ton nhm chia m i tng thnh k cm sao cho mi i tng
thuc v cm c tm gn n nht. S cm k phi c xc nh trc, k c gi tr
nguyn dng.
Thut ton k-means c thc hin qua cc bc sau:
INPUT: Mt CSDL gm n giao tc v s cm k
OUTPUT: Cc cm C
i
(i=1,,k) sao cho hm tiu chun E t gi tr ti thiu
METHOD:
Khi to ngu nhin k tm (centroids) cho k cm.
Repeat
Tnh khong cch gia cc i tng n tng tm.
Gom cc i tng vo cm c tm gn n nht.
Tnh li tm mi cho cc cm mi.
Until Khng cn s thay i tm ca cc cm;
Khong cch gia hai i tng thng c o bng khong cch Euclidean,
Cosine, Tm ca cm thng l trung bnh ca cc i tng trong cm .
Trong gii thut k-means, tham s k (s cm) phi c xc nh trc nn
nh hng rt ln n kt qu phn cm. Kh khn hin nay l cha c gii php
khoa hc no c xem l tt chn tham s ny. C mt s phng php
chn k ph hp nh sau:
- Th mt s gi tr k, da vo cc kt qu thu c la chn k cho kt qu
phn cm tt nht.
- S dng kin ca cc chuyn gia.
- Ly mu v s dng phng php phn cm phn cp xc nh cc tm
khi im.
- La chn nhiu hn k tm sau chn k tm trong s cc tm ny.
- S dng thut ton Bisecting k-means, c th xem chi tit thut ton trong
[17], khng ph thuc vo vic khi to k tm ban u.
27
phc tp ca thut ton k-means l: O(m*k*l*n), vi m l s i tng cn
gom cm, k l s cm, l l s ln lp, n l s thuc tnh ca i tng.
Thut ton k-means kh n gin v c th s dng cho nhiu loi d liu
khc nhau. Thut ton cng kh hiu qu mc d thng phi thc hin chy nhiu
ln. C mt s bin th ca k-means, nh bisecting k-means, c hiu qu cao hn
v t b nh hng bi vn khi to. Tuy nhin, K-means khng ph hp vi mi
loi d liu. N khng th x l cc cm khng c dng hnh cu hoc cc cm c
kch thc v mt khc nhau, mc d vy k-mean thng c th tm cc cm con
thun ty nu c s lng cc cm ln c xc nh. Kh khn ca thut ton
phn cm k-means l d liu cha cc phn t ngoi l. Trong trng hp ny, vic
pht hin v loi b cc i tng ngoi l c th gip ch ng k. Mt hn ch
na ca thut ton k-means l khi nim v tm cm (centroid). Thut ton phn
cm K-medoids khc phc c hn ch ny nhng phc tp cao hn.
1.5.3.2. Thut ton K-medoids
Thut ton K-means ly gi tr trung bnh ca cc i tng trong cm i
din cho cm . Nh vy tm ca cm thng khng l mt i tng thuc cm.
K-means b nh hng nhiu bi cc phn t nhiu v cc phn t ngoi lai.
khc phc hn ch ny mt s nh nghin cu xut thut ton K-medoids. K-
medoids rt ging thut ton k-means ch khc ch k-medoids ly phn t trung
tm nht trong cm lm i din cho cm . Mt s thut ton trong nhm thut
ton K-medoids gm: PAM, CLARA, CLARANS
Chn k i tng bt k lm k tm (medoid).
Repeat
Gom cc i tng vo cm c medoid gn n nht.
Thay th medoid hin ti bng mt i tng khng phi
medoid sao cho cht lng phn cm c ci thin.
Until Cht lng phn cm khng thay i;
Cht lng phn cm c nh gi bng hm chi ph hon chuyn, hm tnh
phi tng t gia medoidvi i tng khng phi medoid trong cm .
28
K-medoids hiu qu hn k-means trong trng hp d liu cha nhiu hay cc
phn t ngoi lai. Nhng so vi k-means th k-medoids c phc tp tnh ton cao hn.
1.5.3.3. Thut ton phn cm phn cp(Hierarchical Methods)
Thut ton phn cm phn cp c nh gi l loi thut ton quan trng th
2 trong cc phng php phn cm. Nh vi k-means, cc phng php ny tng
i c so vi nhiu thut ton phn cm nhng do tnh hiu qu chng vn c s
dng rng ri. C hai hng tip cn phn cm phn cp c bn:
- Gp (agglomerative): Bt u coi mi im thuc mt cm ring l, ti mi
bc thc hin gp cc cp cm gn nhau nht. K thut ny cn xc nh mt khi
nim s gn nhau gia cc cm.
- Chia(divisive): Bt u vi mt cm bao gm tt c cc i tng, ti mi
bc, chia mt cm cho ti khi ch khng cn cm no cn phi chia na. K thut
ny i hi phi c tiu chun quyt nh cm cn phn chia ti mi bc v lm
th no thc hin chia tch.
K thut gp vn c s dng ph bin cho n nay. phn ny tc gi xin
tp trung trnh by k thut ny.
Phng php phn cm phn cp thng c hin th trc quan bng cch s
dng mt s dng cy gi l dendrogram, s ny cn biu din c c mi
quan h gia cm cha - cm con v th t cc cm c gp/chia.
Thut ton c bn thc hin nh sau:
Tnh ma trn xp x,
Coi mi i tng l mt cm,
Repeat
Gp hai cm gn nhau nht,
Tnh li ma trn xp x,
Until c mt cm duy nht.
Nhim v chnh trong phng php ny l tnh gi tr xp x gia hai cm.
Mi thut ton xc nh mt cch ring o khong cch gia cc cm.C ba
cch c dng ph bin tnh khong cch l:
29
MIN (Single link): khong cch gia hai cm l khong cch gia hai i
tng gn nhau nht thuc 2 cm.
MAX (complete link):khong cch gia hai cm l khong cch gia hai i
tng xa nhau nht thuc 2 cm.
Group average:khong cch gia hai cm l khong cch trung bnh gia cc
i tng thuc 2 cm.
Cc thut ton phn cm phn cp gp tn km v cc yu cu tnh ton v
khng gian lu tr. Trong thc t php gp c th gy cc vn v nhiu, c bit
vi d liu nhiu thuc tnh (high-dimensional data), chng hn d liu vn bn.
Hai kh khn ny c th c gii quyt mt mc no bi phn cm tng
phn d liu s dng k thut khc, chng hn nh K-means.
1.6. KT LUN
Chng mt gii thiu tng quan v KPDL: cc m hnh KPDL v cc khi
nim c bn lin quan n qu trnh tm tp MDL thng xuyn. Tc gi tp
trung nghin cu v gii thiu mt s thut ton kinh in nh: Apriori, Partition,
FP-Growth, Mi thut ton u c v d c th minh ha vi cng mt bng d
liu ban u, th hin tng bc thc hin thut ton v kt qu u ra. Chng mt
cng tp trung nghin cu v gii thiu v phn cm, cc loi o nh gi
tng t gia hai i tng v cc phng php phn cm d liu cng cc
thut ton phn cm in hnh ca tng phng php.
Trong qu trnh nghin cu v ci t cc thut ton, tc gi nhn thy rng,
vi d liu c kch thc nh th vic a ton b d liu vo b nh trong vi cu
trc con tr s x l nhanh hn l b nh ngoi vi cu trc tp tin. Tuy nhin,
vi tc pht trin v ng dng CNTT hin nay, hu ht cc hot ng ca con
ngi u c thc hin qua internet v pht sinh d liu. Theo IBM thng k, d
liu mi c to ra trong 2 nm gn y chim n 90% khi lng d liu t
trc n nay. Theo thi gian, d liu ny bt u vt qu kh nng x l ca cc
my tnh n. V vy, hng tip cn pht trin cc thut ton khai ph d liu song
song c nhiu nh nghin cu quan tm v ci thin ng k hiu sut khai ph.
Ngoi ra, cu hnh ca my tnh cng lm thay i tc ca cc thut ton.

Chng 2. THUT TON KHAI PH TP THNG XUYN
HIU QU S DNG K THUT PHN CM
Chng hai tc gi tp trung nghin cu v trnh by thut
ton khai ph tp thng xuyn hiu qu bng vic s dng k
thut phn cm d liu (Efficient Algorithm For Mining Frequent
Itemsets Using Clustering Techniques) c D.Kerana Hanirex
v Dr.M.A Dorai Rangaswamy pht trin nm 2011 trong [21].
Trnh by ni dung thut ton, cc th tc ci t chnh v v d
minh ha cho thut ton.
2.1. M U
Apriori l thut ton kinh in v khai ph tp thng xuyn. Tuy nhin
Apriori cn tn ti hai nt tht (bottleneck):
- Pht sinh s lng ln TUV.
- Phi duyt ton b CSDL qu nhiu ln tnh h tr ca cc MDL v
cc tp MDL ng vin
Thut ton Apriori khng th gii c khi d liu ln. Da vo Apriori, c
nhiu thut ton c thit k vi nhng sa i v ci tin. Hai cch tip cn chnh
nhm khc phc hai hn ch trn: Mt l lm gim bt s ln duyt qua ton b
CSDL, hoc thay th ton b CSDL vi ch mt phn ca n (cc cm, cc lp); hai
l dng k thut xn bt lm gim s lng TUV.
Nm 2011, D.Kerana Hanirex v Dr.M.A Dorai Rangaswamy pht trin mt
thut ton khai ph tp thng xuyn hiu qu s dng k thut phn cm. Da vo
k thut phn hoch cm d liu chia CSDL thnh cc cm (Thut ton PAFI
Partition Algorithm for Mining Frequent Item sets) sau p dng mt ci tin ca
thut ton Apriori khai ph tp thng xuyn trn cc cm thay v phi khai ph
trn c CSDL ln.
31
2.2. NI DUNG THUT TON
2.2.1. Phn cm v phn hoch
Phn cm l k thut khai ph d liu c s dng phn chia cc giao tc
trong CSDL T vo cc cm sao cho cc giao tc tng t nhau c gom vo
mt cm, cc giao tc khng tng t c gom vo cc cm khc nhau.
Phn hoch d liu l k thut nn tng ca rt nhiu cc thut ton khai ph
song song cng nh cc thut ton khai ph phn tn. Da trn mt nhn xt n
gin l: Mt tp MDL l thng xuyn th n phi thng xuyn trong t nht mt
phn hoch, da trn tng ny nhiu thut ton KPDL hiu qu c thit k.
Kt hp k thut phn hoch v phn cm, cc thut ton khai ph song song
v phn tn d dng c thit k vi mi cm c th c x l bi mt my
ring bit.
Khi CSDL c phn hoch, kch thc ca cc cm nh hn rt nhiu so vi
kch thc ca CSDL nn c th a ton b cm vo b nh trong tm tp
thng xuyn trn cm . Nh vy, hiu sut khai ph s c ci thin.
Thut ton PAFI s dng k thut phn hoch phn cm CSDL. S lng
cm (NOC Number Of Cluster) c tnh da vo t l gia s lng cc giao tc
ca CSDL (COT Count Of Transaction) vi mt s t nhin N bt k.
Thut ton bao gm cc bc sau:
- Tm tm cho cc cm: Gi di ca giao tc l s lng cc MDL trong
giao tc . Chn giao tc di nht lm tm cho cm th nht, chn giao tc di th
hai lm tm cho cm th hai, Lp li cho n khi mi cm u c tm.

3.6. KT LUN
Trng tm ca lun vn tp trung chng 3. Tc gi pht trin mt thut
ton khai ph tp thng xuyn da vo s phn hoch cm d liu, thut ton khai
ph tp thng xuyn nhanh (QFIM) c v d minh ha c th r rng tng bc
ca thut ton. Vi k thut phn hoch cm d liu, thut ton QFIM m bo tnh
dng v song song ha qu trnh khai ph tp thng xuyn.
Thut ton QFIM l thut ton pht trin trn nn tng thut ton Apriori, vi
hng nghin cu c gng lm gim kch thc CSDL cn duyt khi tnh h tr
ca cc TUV v song song ha qu trnh khai ph.
Nh bit, thut ton Apriori, mi ln tnh h tr ca mt TUV l mt
ln duyt CSDL giao tc. Vic phn hoch cc giao tc vo cc cm nh, sao cho
mi ln tnh h tr ch cn duyt cm tng ng l mt hng ci tin nhm
nng cao hiu qu khai ph ca Apriori. Thut ton QFIM c khi lng tnh ton
nh hn, chy nhanh hn thut ton Apriori rt nhiu vi l do sau:
- Phn hoch CSDL thnh k cm nh, vic khai ph tp thng xuyn c th
thc hin song song trn k my tnh ring l.
